title: Congratulations to MAgIC lab undergraduate student Qinxiao Ma for being awarded as an outstanding graduate
description: Qinxiao Ma joined the MAgIC lab in 2022 and conducted research in MRAC and Flapping-wing aircraft under the supervision of Prof. Yang Wang. He graduated in June 2023 with the title of Outstanding Undergraduate Student of University of ShanghaiTech. Qinxiao Ma will continue his research on flapping-wing aircraft control and other robotics projects in Prof. Yang Wang's research groop.
